-- LVMH to Buy 70% of Online Fragrance Retailer Sack's to Expand in Brazil
-- David Whitehouse
-- 2010-07-02T04:47:35Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-02/lvmh-agrees-to-acquire-70-of-brazilian-online-fragrance-retailer-sack-s.html

          
          
              LVMH Moet Hennessy Louis Vuitton SA
said it will buy 70 percent of online fragrance retailer Sack’s
to expand in Brazil.  
 Sack’s current management will stay in place, LVMH said in
a statement on Business Wire, without giving the price.  
          
          


  


        